          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I started sharing our three day itinerary in Bruges in my "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://www.everydayaccountsblog.com/2016/06/travel-with-me-bruges-in-three-days-part-1-of-1/",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "part 1 post"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " last week. Today I'm finishing out that itinerary. Bruges has so much to see and do! I have a ton of pictures to share in this post as well because we couldn't stop taking them.  We were just so smitten with this place!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
