      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "De Halve Maan Brewery"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "De Halve Maan is a very old, well-known Belgian brewery based in Bruges. We booked tickets for an afternoon tour because we are planners who book everything in advance, and we were glad we did. The tours sell out quickly, and both the Flemish and English tour groups were fully booked when we arrived."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The tour was great - the guide took us throughout the whole brewery, which was perfectly set up for tours and for teaching about the brewing process."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/20160130_143231-1024x576.jpg",
              "alt": "20160130_143231",
              "title": null
            },
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://www.everydayaccountsblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/20160130_143231.jpg",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "As part of the tour, you eventually make your way up to the top of the building and see great views of the city."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
