      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "After the tour, you are released in the tasting room where you get several tastings. We had a good time meeting some other travelers at our table and exchanging travel stories."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/20160130_153433-1024x576.jpg",
              "alt": "20160130_153433",
              "title": null
            },
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://www.everydayaccountsblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/20160130_153433.jpg",
                  "title": null
