          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Walking Tour"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "We had to slip out of the tasting at the brewery a bit early to catch the start time of our walking tour. We booked a free evening walking tour that came with our Bruges City Card. We met our guide at 't Zand Square, a part of the city we hadn't been to yet."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/2016-01-30-16.52.01-1024x768.jpg",
              "alt": "2016-01-30 16.52.01",
              "title": null
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "On the way to our first stop, we passed this beautiful pond filled with swans. There is a very interesting legend about the swans in Bruges, and the city embraces it."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/2016-01-30-13.54.35-1024x768.jpg",
              "alt": "2016-01-30 13.54.35",
              "title": null
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "One of the first stops on the tour was the Bruges Béguinage. A béguinage is a complex that houses women who are religious but don't make any formal vows and are free to leave whenever they want. This particular complex (called Ten Wijngaerde) was founded in the 13th century, but it no longer houses Beguines. Since 1927, it has been a convent for Benedictine nuns. Visitors are allowed but are asked to keep quiet."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/20160130_135756-1024x576.jpg",
              "alt": "20160130_135756",
              "title": null
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " Our guide did a decent job telling us the history of the city as we walked around, although she was sometimes hard to understand because of her accent."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
