      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Our tour ended in the same square where it began, right by the 't Zand Square fountain."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Fish Market Restaurant"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "On the recommendation of our walking tour guide, we made our way back to the Fish Market area for dinner. We were a little hesitant given the prices we saw on the menus, but we really wanted to try one of the Bruges restaurants loved by locals and famous for its seafood."
          }
        ]
      },
