      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Day 3"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To start out day 3, Daniel went to the chocolate museum, and I stayed home to plan out and book the end of our 2.5 month Europe trip. We had recently made the decision to end our trip with three weeks in Italy, something we originally weren't sure we were going to do."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Choco Story"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Daniel had a nice morning at the chocolate museum. He says it's worth doing (especially if you have the Bruges City Card), but it's not amazing."
          }
        ]
