          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I got the speculoos waffle, and Daniel got a caramel one. They were nice and hot and full of amazing flavor. I cannot recommend the Arlecchino Gelateria on Burg Square enough!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
